%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c1471%2c20220429%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,111,交簡,1471,20220429,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"交簡","JNO":"1471","JDATE":"20220429","JTITLE":"公共危險"}